 4. the person eating lime is somewhere to the left of the project-manager##5
 5. the farmhouse house is on the left or right of the person eating potato##3
 6. the tower house is in an odd position##4
 7. the doctor is on the left or right of the tower house##3
 8. the person eating banana is somewhere to the right of the analyst##5
 9. the doctor is on the left or right of the person watching epic movies##3
10. the accountant is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
11. the person watching drama movies is somewhere to the right of the tower house##5
12. the person eating lime is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3      |        4        |
| House      | tower   | ranch-style | victorian   | farmhouse          |
| Food          | lime    | radish        | potato     | banana          |
| Job           | analyst | doctor        | accountant | project-manager |
| Movie-Genre   | epic    | adventure     | drama      | disaster        |

