.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-20::.
There 4 different types of food: blueberry, lime, tomato, watermelon
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, guinea-pig, frog, cat
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, comedy, drama, martial-arts
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, gospel, punk, soul
 1. the person eating tomato is somewhere to the right of the person watching comedy movies##5
 2. the fan of soul is the person eating blueberry##1
 3. the person eating tomato is somewhere to the left of the fan of electronic##5
 4. the owner of the hedgehog is in an even position##4
 5. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the fan of punk##1
 6. the fan of electronic is somewhere to the right of the fan of gospel##5
 7. the owner of the frog is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 8. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hedgehog##5
 9. the fan of punk is on the right of the person eating blueberry##1
10. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the right of the person eating tomato##5
11. the person watching action movies is somewhere to the right of the person eating watermelon##5
12. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the left of the person eating tomato##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |     4      |
| Food          | blueberry | tomato  | watermelon    | lime       |
| Pet           | guinea-pig  | cat | frog | hedgehog  |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy    | drama   | martial-arts  | action     |
| Music-Genre   | soul      | punk    | gospel        | electronic |

 